AS YOU CHOOSE.                  

202
00:16:33,792 --> 00:16:36,093
            WELL ?              

203
00:16:36,162 --> 00:16:39,129
    THAT'S TWICE                
    YOU INVITED ME TO LEAVE.    
<i>THAT'S RIGHT.</i>                   

204
00:16:39,198 --> 00:16:43,333
