THAT YOU'RE A SLOW-WITTED       
COUNTRY BOY, I'LL PUT YOU OUT ! 

205
00:16:43,402 --> 00:16:46,303
    YOU'RE PRETTY TOUGH, HUH ?  

206
00:16:46,372 --> 00:16:49,473
