214
00:17:16,935 --> 00:17:22,172
    I'D LIKE TO APOLOGIZE       
    FOR BEING SO... HOSTILE.    
    THAT'S THE WORD, ISN'T IT ? 

215
00:17:22,241 --> 00:17:25,442
