229
00:18:27,506 --> 00:18:29,706
    WHAT ARE YOU                
    THINKING, GLENN ?           

230
00:18:31,477 --> 00:18:34,511
        ABOUT THE DREAMS        
        I USED TO HAVE.         

231
00:18:34,580 --> 00:18:38,248
        OF MONEY, FAME.         

232
00:18:38,317 --> 00:18:41,084
    IS THAT WHAT                
    YOU WANT ?                  

233
00:18:43,855 --> 00:18:46,923
