235
00:18:57,236 --> 00:19:00,804
            LISTEN, MA'AM,      
            MY MA WAS ENSLAVED  
            ON OUR FARM.        

236
00:19:00,872 --> 00:19:03,640
            <i> I DO MEAN ENSLAVED.</i>

237
00:19:03,709 --> 00:19:07,211
        MANY TIMES              
        I'VE SEEN HER...        

238
00:19:07,279 --> 00:19:09,946
