00:21:05,431 --> 00:21:08,998
    HER DEATH WAS A QUICK ONE.  

268
00:21:10,336 --> 00:21:12,569
    DID YOU WANT                
    TO GO TO COLLEGE, GLENN ?   

269
00:21:14,973 --> 00:21:20,009
