    THE HEART'S OUT OF IT,      
    AND I'LL LEAVE.             

270
00:21:20,078 --> 00:21:22,212
        COULD I COME BACK       
        ANOTHER TIME ?          

271
00:21:22,280 --> 00:21:24,914
    OH, OF COURSE.              

272
00:21:24,983 --> 00:21:27,250
    MONDAY, AROUND NOON ?       

273
00:21:29,154 --> 00:21:31,355
