1088
01:22:43,524 --> 01:22:46,024
A VERY SMALL WORLD.             

1089
01:22:46,092 --> 01:22:49,661
I'LL BORROW THIS,               
IF I MAY.                       

1090
01:22:49,730 --> 01:22:52,731
