1099
01:23:20,828 --> 01:23:23,462
        I DON'T MEAN TO BE      
        DISRESPECTFUL TO YOU,   

1100
01:23:25,198 --> 01:23:28,333
    BUT I'M IN LOVE WITH YOU,   
    IRENE.                      

1101
01:23:30,738 --> 01:23:32,587
        I'M IN LOVE WITH YOU.   

1102
01:24:52,486 --> 01:24:54,419
<i>[ Door Opens ]</i>                  

1103
01:26:55,876 --> 01:26:58,142
