1110
01:28:21,594 --> 01:28:23,528
        IT'S VERY IMPORTANT.    

1111
01:28:23,596 --> 01:28:26,898
        YES,                    
        I'LL LEAVE THE MESSAGE. 

1112
01:28:29,569 --> 01:28:33,504
    MISS IRENE, THAT BOY SOUNDS 
