1113
01:28:33,573 --> 01:28:35,874
        IT'S THE THIRD TIME     
        HE'S CALLED.            

1114
01:28:50,490 --> 01:28:52,623
                HERE'S TO US.   

1115
01:28:55,262 --> 01:28:59,130
OF COURSE, I'M ASSUMING         
THAT YOUR WIFE IS STILL WILLING 
TO GIVE YOU A DIVORCE.          

1116
01:28:59,199 --> 01:29:02,834
