    ABOUT THAT.  YOU KNOW       
    SHE'D JUMP AT THE CHANCE.   

1117
01:29:02,903 --> 01:29:05,436
        IN ONE STROKE,          
        YOU'VE GIVEN MY LIFE    
        REAL MEANIN'.           

1118
01:29:07,975 --> 01:29:09,908
