I HAVE TO SAY TO YOU.           

1119
01:29:09,977 --> 01:29:13,078
    WHAT ELSE IS THERE TO SAY ? 
    YOU'RE GOING TO MARRY ME.   

1120
01:29:15,015 --> 01:29:17,148
    I DON'T--                   

1121
01:29:17,217 --> 01:29:19,617
