SCHOOLKIDS.                     

1125
01:29:31,531 --> 01:29:35,800
        I'M RUNNING AWAY        
        FROM SOMETHING--        
        SOMETHING I'M AFRAID OF.

1126
01:29:37,137 --> 01:29:40,238
            ANOTHER MAN.        

1127
01:29:40,307 --> 01:29:43,108
ANYONE-- ANYONE I KNOW ?        

1128
01:29:43,176 --> 01:29:46,111
    THAT-THAT'S UNIMPORTANT.    
    IT'S JUST THAT...           

1129
01:29:46,179 --> 01:29:50,181
