I'VE BEEN TERRIBLY FRIGHTENED.  

1130
01:29:50,250 --> 01:29:53,351
    IN FACT, I'VE FELT MYSELF   
    ON THE BRINK--              

1131
01:29:53,420 --> 01:29:56,288
