SAYING IS UNIMPORTANT.          

1132
01:29:56,356 --> 01:29:58,990
I KNOW YOU'LL BE                
A WONDERFUL WIFE.               

1133
01:30:00,527 --> 01:30:04,329
            WE'LL BE HAPPY.     
