1141
01:30:31,458 --> 01:30:34,859
            <i> NO, NO.</i>            
            <i> NOT YOU, MR. LEWIS.</i>
            <i> I'M SORRY.</i>         

1142
01:30:42,202 --> 01:30:45,736
