ALONG THE LINE.                 

1147
01:31:02,990 --> 01:31:05,223
            WHAT'S THAT         
            SUPPOSED TO MEAN ?  

1148
01:31:05,292 --> 01:31:08,293
            [ Engine Revs ]     
        [ Inaudible ]           

1149
01:31:12,165 --> 01:31:16,667
