1151
01:31:21,574 --> 01:31:24,442
    I DON'T KNOW.               
    I'D LIKE TO GO HOME MYSELF. 

1152
01:31:27,214 --> 01:31:29,914
        NICE TO SEE YOU, SON,   
        MA'AM.                  

