01:32:51,731 --> 01:32:53,664
        [ Ringing ]             

1166
01:32:57,971 --> 01:32:59,937
<i>WOULD YOU TELL MRS. SPEERY</i>      
<i>I'D LIKE TO SEE HER ?</i>           

1167
01:33:00,006 --> 01:33:01,939
<i>OR IS HER CAR HOME</i>              
<i>AND SHE ISN'T ?</i>                 

