BUT SHE'S EXPECTING SOMEBODY.   

1169
01:33:04,277 --> 01:33:07,479
        NEVER MIND, SARAH.      
        ASK HIM TO COME IN.     

1170
01:33:22,262 --> 01:33:24,395
WOULD YOU SIT DOWN ?            

1171
01:33:27,867 --> 01:33:30,502
