IS THIS-- IS HE WHAT            
YOU'RE RUNNIN' AWAY FROM ?      

1207
01:35:44,938 --> 01:35:48,173
    YOU'VE GOT NO RIGHT TO TALK 
    TO HER LIKE THAT, MR. MACY. 
HAVEN'T I ?                     

1208
01:35:48,241 --> 01:35:51,609
