1210
01:36:05,825 --> 01:36:10,195
IF I FIND YOUR SON AROUND,      
HE'LL GET SHIPPED HOME IN A BOX.
DON'T SAY I DIDN'T WARN YOU.    

1211
01:36:10,263 --> 01:36:13,131
- GLENN--                       
